  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<b>Project Manager:</b> DrDragren\r\n\r\n<b>Front End Developer:</b> DrDragren\r\n<b>Back
    End Developer:</b> LostKey09\r\n\r\n<b>Lead Art Director:</b> DrDragren\r\n<b>Technical
    Art Director:</b> DrDragren\r\n<b>Artist:</b> DrDragren\r\n\r\n<b>Lead Game Designer:</b>
    Rabu\r\n<b>Associate Game Designer:</b> GZPY\r\n\r\nSome art used in this project
    were from the following:\r\n\u201C<i>Modern City Backgrounds Pixel Art</i>\u201D
    created by <b>CraftPix.Net</b>\r\n\r\nFonts used in this project were from the
    following:\r\n\u201C<i>Pixelated Elegance Font</i>\u201D designed by <b>GGBotNet</b>
    and made with PixelForge\r\n\u201C<i>Raster Forge Font</i>\u201D designed by
    <b>GGBotNet</b>\r\n\r\nSome of the sounds in this project were from the following:\r\n\u201C<i>Universal
    UI Soundpack</i>\u201D created and distributed by </b>Nathan Gibson</b>\r\n\u201C<i>Pixel
    Forge Jam Music</i>\u201D provided by <b>QKing</b>\r\n\u201C<i>UI and Item sounds
    Sample 1</i>\u201D created by <b>ViRiX Dreamcore (David McKee) <u>soundcloud.com/virix</u></b>\r\n\"<i>The
    Essential Retro Video Game Sound Effects Collection [512 sounds]</i>\" created
    by <b>Juhani Junkala</b>\r\n\u201C<i>Select 003</i>\u201D created by <b>CreatorsHome</b>\r\n\u201C<i>UI
    Radio Select</i>\u201D created by <b>SoundShelfStudio</b>\r\n\r\nSpecial thanks
    to our playtesters:\r\n..."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 187a34e75096667488a027fec7939ea8, type: 2}
